                organizer      family                 extended family
                                                      graph, limited
                                                      social features

  FamilyWall    Family         Privacy-focused        Niche, limited
                organizer                             network effect, no
                                                      commerce layer

  Tinybeans     Baby/child     Strong for new parents Age-limited use
                sharing                               case, no extended
                                                      family coordination

  GroupMe /     Messaging      Universal adoption     No structure, no
  WhatsApp                                            events, no
                                                      relationship graph,
                                                      no commerce

  Ancestry      Genealogy      Deep family history    Historical only, no
                                                      live coordination or
                                                      communication

  23andMe       DNA /          Biological data        Not a coordination
                genealogy      insight                platform; different
                                                      use case entirely
  ------------- -------------- ---------------------- --------------------

Market gap confirmed: No product combines (1) extended family
relationship graph, (2) private event and calendar coordination, (3)
multi-generational accessibility, and (4) a natural commerce layer. This
is the white space FamLink occupies.

